character.name: Astolfo
character.wikiDescription: Astolfo (アストルフォ, Asutorufo), Class Name Rider of "Black" ("黒"のライダー, "Kuro" no Raidā), is the Rider-class Servant of Celenike Icecolle Yggdmillennia of the Black Faction in the Great Holy Grail War of Fate/Apocrypha. After the death of Celenike, he forms a contract with Sieg. He is one of the Servants of Ritsuka Fujimaru of the Grand Order conflicts of Fate/Grand Order. He is a part of Hakuno Kishinami's army in Fate/EXTELLA LINK.

character.name: Bridget
character.wikiDescription: Bridget is a recurring character in the Guilty Gear series. Born to wealthy parents, Bridget has become a bounty hunter to refute her village's superstitions regarding twins. Wielding a yo-yo in battle, she fights alongside a mysterious teddy bear called Roger.

character.name: Venti
character.wikiDescription: Venti is a playable Anemo character in Genshin Impact. He is a free-spirited, wine-loving bard of Mondstadt, belying his identity as Barbatos, the Anemo Archon.

character.name: Midare Toushirou
character.wikiDescription: Midare Toushirou is one of the Awataguchi blades. Midare is notable for looking rather like a girl and being a bit of a tease. He meets his previous master Hosokawa Katsumoto, and realizes that humans are flawed. Midare gets worried that the Saniwa will become flawed as well, so he returns, changed.

character.name: Aether
character.wikiDescription: Aether, also known as the Traveler and the Outlander, is the main protagonist and player character of the 2020 action role-playing fantasy video game Genshin Impact, as well as a cameo character in its accompanying webcomic series of the same name.

character.name: Fujisaki Chihiro
character.wikiDescription: Chihiro Fujisaki (不二咲 千尋), is a student in Hope's Peak Academy's Class 78th, and a participant of the Killing School Life featured in Danganronpa: Trigger Happy Havoc. Chihiro's title is the Ultimate Programmer (超高校級の「プログラマー」 lit. Super High School Level Programmer).

character.name: Rimuru Tempest
character.wikiDescription: Rimuru Tempest (リムル゠テンペスト rimuru tenpesuto?) is the main protagonist of That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime and the reincarnation of Satoru Mikami.

character.name: Xingqiu
character.wikiDescription: Xingqiu (Chinese: 行秋 Xíngqiū) is a playable Hydro character in Genshin Impact. He is the second son of the Guild Manager of the Feiyun Commerce Guild, an influential group in Liyue, and is also a self-proclaimed practitioner of the Guhua Clan's arts. Also an avid reader, Xingqiu aims to be the embodiment of chivalry like the heroes from the books he reads; however, this belies his knack for mischief.

character.name: Chongyun
character.wikiDescription: Chongyun (Chinese: 重云 Chóngyún) is a playable Cryo character in Genshin Impact. Born with an excess of yang (positive) energy, Chongyun has become a highly effective exorcist in Liyue — so effective to the point where he hasn't seen a spirit himself, as they immediately flee when he approaches. The excessive yang energy also makes him particularly susceptible to heat and strong emotion, which has led to some rather unexpected results.

character.name: Oyama Mahiro
character.wikiDescription: Mahiro Oyama (緒山 真尋, Oyama Mahiro) is a former otaku slacker and the brother-turned-sister of Mihari Oyama, having been transformed into a middle-school aged girl by one of Mihari's experiments. She is voiced by Marika Kōno in the anime.

character.name: Kanzaki Hideri
character.wikiDescription: Hideri Kanzaki (神崎 ひでり Kanzaki Hideri) is Cafe Stile's fifth addition, hired for "his" adorable looks. The staff gets largely surprised, and it's not because Hideri plays an idol singer, yet never sings.

character.name: Shikanoin Heizou
character.wikiDescription: Shikanoin Heizou (Japanese: 鹿野院平蔵 Shikanoin Heizou) is a playable Anemo character in Genshin Impact. He is the number one Tenryou Commission detective, harboring a rivalry with the Bantan Sango Detective Agency's Sango.

character.name: Scaramouche (Wanderer)
character.wikiDescription: The Balladeer, also known as Scaramouche and Kunikuzushi (Japanese: 国崩), was the Sixth of the Eleven Fatui Harbingers and one of Genshin Impact's antagonists. Scaramouche is a prototype puppet created as a proof of concept to test Raiden Ei's plans for an indestructible, Gnosis-bearing puppet.

character.name: Lio Fotia
character.wikiDescription: Lio Fotia (リオ・フォーティア) is the current leader of Mad Burnish. He starts off as the false antagonist of Promare. He later acts as the film's deuteragonist.

character.name: Tighnari
character.wikiDescription: Tighnari is a playable Dendro character in Genshin Impact. Tighnari is the stern Chief Officer of the Forest Rangers and Collei's mentor. Despite his intelligence, he prefers to live a solitary life in the depths of Avidya Forest rather than in the ivory tower of Sumeru Akademiya.

character.name: Shimakaze
character.wikiDescription: Shimakaze (島風, Island Wind) is a character and one of the heroes from the Kantai Collection series who was implemented into the game on the 23rd of April, 2013.

character.name: Felix Argyle
character.wikiDescription: Felix Argyle (フェリックス・アーガイル), commonly known as Ferris (フェリス), is Crusch Karsten's knight. Debuting in Arc 3, he played a rather vital role as Crusch's knight and supported Subaru in his fight against the Hakugei and Sin Archbishop of Sloth. Though not present in the following 4th Arc, he reappeared in Arc 5 and yet again played a vital role for Crusch's character development.

character.name: Kaedehara Kazuha
character.wikiDescription: Kaedehara Kazuha (Japanese: 楓原万葉 Kaedehara Kazuha) is a playable Anemo character in Genshin Impact. A wandering samurai of the once-famed Kaedehara Clan with an ability to read the sounds of nature, Kazuha is a temporary crewmember of The Crux. Despite being burdened by the many happenings of his past, Kazuha still maintains an easygoing disposition.

character.name: Gorou
character.wikiDescription: Gorou (Japanese: ゴロー Goroo) is a playable Geo character in Genshin Impact. He is a general of the Watatsumi Army. Courageous and reliable, his men know they can place their trust in him both on and off of the battlefield.

character.name: Akiyama Mizuki
character.wikiDescription: Akiyama Mizuki (暁山瑞希) is a first year student at Kamiyama High School. They're the animator of the underground music circle 25-ji, Nightcord de., going by the alias "Amia".

character.name: Urushibara Ruka
character.wikiDescription: Luka Urushibara (漆原るか Urushibara Ruka) is a close friend and classmate of Mayuri Shiina and so-called protégé of Rintaro Okabe. While feminine in appearance and personality, Luka is a male on most worldlines. Mayuri often attempts to coerce him into cosplaying. He works at the Yanabayashi Shrine as a shrine maiden.

character.name: Totsuka Saika
character.wikiDescription: Saika Totsuka (戸塚 彩加 Totsuka Saika) is a student of Class 2F in Sobu High School and a president of the school's Tennis Club.

character.name: Lyney
character.wikiDescription: Lyney is a playable Pyro character in Genshin Impact. Skilled and eloquent, Lyney is Fontaine's Great Magician and Lynette's twin brother. After their parents' death and having been saved from an abusive noble by their "Father," Lyney has undertaken missions for the House of the Hearth and has said that he will eventually become the successor of "Father."

character.name: Freminet
character.wikiDescription: Freminet is a playable Cryo character in Genshin Impact. Despite his skill and experience as a professional diver, Freminet prefers to stay out of the spotlight, content to simply carry out orders and find peace next to the Tidalga and Romaritime Flowers underwater.

character.name: Mihate Hiura
character.wikiDescription: Hiura Mihate was born on September 10th. Hiura is an Otaku and is childhood friends with a very popular guy in his school named Kenshirou Midou.

character.name: Shiota Nagisa
character.wikiDescription: Nagisa Shiota (潮田 渚, Shiota Nagisa) is a student in Korosensei's Class 3-E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School and the main protagonist and narrator of Assassination Classroom. Despite his overall passive nature, Nagisa has a natural talent for assassination.

character.name: Arikawa Hime
character.wikiDescription: Hime Arikawa (有川 ひめ, Arikawa Hime) is a second year student at Shimoshina High School who is forced to dress up as a girl to pay off his creditors after the Student Council save him from the Yakuza Debt Collectors.

character.name: Gasper Vladi
character.wikiDescription: Gasper Vladi is one of the male protagonists of High School DxD. He is a cross-dressing male Dhampir, a half-Vampire half-human but was turned into a Devil by Rias Gremory. He has the ability to stop time and is Rias' first Bishop.
